Package com.quantcomponents.marketdata

Interface Summary
IMarketDataManager Main service interface to create and manage market data time-series
IMarketDataProvider Low-level interface to be implemented by broker adapters to deal with market data
IMarketDataProvider.IMarketDepthListener Listener of price book updates
IMarketDataProvider.IRealTimeDataListener Listener of realtime price bars
IMarketDataProvider.ITickListener Listener of realtime price ticks
IMutableOHLCTimeSeries Mutable version of IOHLCTimeSeries
IMutableTickTimeSeries Mutable version of ITickTimeSeries
IMutableTimeSeries<P extends ISeriesPoint<Date,Double>> A mutable series based on Date and Double
IOHLC OHLC bar interface.
IOHLCPoint OHLC data-point
IOHLCTimeSeries Time series containing only OHLC points
IStockDatabase High level object to collect historical and realtime data about a specific contract.
IStockDatabaseContainer Container for stock databases.
IStockDataCollection Generic interface for all the collection types related to a specific contract Its use in the framework is to narrow down the type of a series to a contract price series
ITickPoint Tick data point
ITickTimeSeries Time series containing only tick data points
ITimeSeries<P extends ISeriesPoint<Date,Double>> Specific time series containing double values, indexed by Date
ITimeSeriesListener Specific listener for time series
 

Class Summary
MemoryStockDatabaseContainer Simple non-persistent implementation class for a IStockDatabaseContainer It can be used as default service when no better containerr are available
OHLCPoint OHLC point implementation
OHLCPointAccumulator An implementation of IOHLCPoint that consolidates tick data Each time the OHLCPointAccumulator.addTick(ITickPoint) method is called, the value of this data-point is updated.
OHLCTimeSeries Implementation of a mutable OHLC time series
OHLCVirtualTimeSeries Virtual OHLC time series.
StockDatabase Implementation of IStockDatabase
TickPoint Implementation of ITickPoint
TickTimeSeries Specialized time series for tick data
TimeSeries<P extends ISeriesPoint<Date,Double>> Specialized mutable time series containing double values, indexed by Date
TimeSeriesBetween<P extends ISeriesPoint<Date,Double>> Operator that extracts a snapshot subset of a time series, specified by start and end indexes
TimeSeriesSince<P extends ISeriesPoint<Date,Double>> Operator that extracts a snapshot subset of a time series, specified by start index, up to the end of the source series
TimeSeriesTail<P extends ISeriesPoint<Date,Double>> Operator that extracts a snapshot subset of a time series, specified by a number of points from the tail of the series
